# Module: tf.saved_model.main_op



Defined in [`tensorflow/python/saved_model/main_op.py`](https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.4/tensorflow/python/saved_model/main_op.py).

SavedModel main op.

Builds a main op that defines the sequence of ops to be run as part of the
SavedModel load/restore operations.

## Functions

[`main_op(...)`](../../tf/saved_model/main_op/main_op): Returns a main op to init variables and tables.

[`main_op_with_restore(...)`](../../tf/saved_model/main_op/main_op_with_restore): Returns a main op to init variables, tables and restore the graph.
